Package: diffp4
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Diff coloring tool for Perforce (p4)
 Diff coloring output text from Perforce (p4) tool.
 As p4 doesn't have capability (without making some modification e.g. P4DIFF
 environment variable) to color diff-formate text output. This tool will help
 do so.
